---
// Cost of freedom — electric vs petrol
---

<section class="section cost-section">
  <div class="container cost-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Cost of freedom</span>
      <h2>Cheaper to run. By a lot.</h2>
      <p class="cost-lead">Electricity costs a fraction of petrol. No oil changes, no winterisation, no engine service. Over a season, the savings pay for the drive.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn">Calculate your savings</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-compare">
      <div class="cost-row petrol">
        <div class="cost-label">
          <strong>Petrol</strong>
          <span>per hour</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cost-amount">€24.80</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-row electric">
        <div class="cost-label">
          <strong>Sylents</strong>
          <span>per hour</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cost-amount">€1.20</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-saving">
        <span>Over a 50-hour season</span>
        <strong>~€1,180 saved</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.cost-section {
  background: var(--color-bg-section);
  border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.cost-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.cost-lead {
  max-width: 480px;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin: 1.25rem 0 2rem;
}
.cost-compare {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.cost-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.cost-row.petrol { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
.cost-row.electric { background: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.08); border-color: var(--color-border-strong); }
.cost-label { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.cost-label strong { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-light); }
.cost-label span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
.cost-amount { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-light); }
.cost-row.electric .cost-amount { color: var(--color-primary); }
.cost-saving {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.cost-saving span { color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
.cost-saving strong { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-accent); }
@media (max-width: 800px) {
  .cost-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}
</style>
